ie.gmit.sw.result

Interface Resultable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Result

    public interface Resultable

    Resultable

    Interface specifies methods common to all Result type objects that inherit from this class. These are getters/ setters for key, score and plain text.
    Since:
    01/01/2016
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    John Malcolm Anderson
    See Also:
    Result, ResultConsumer
